The presidential rally of the All Progressives Congress (APC) was held in Borno state on Saturday. It was a homecoming for Kashim Shettima, the APC vice presidential candidate and former state governor. Shettima served as governor from 2011 to 2019. Among those present at the rally were Bola Tinubu, APC presidential candidate; Ali Modu Sheriff, former governor of Borno, and Abdullahi Adamu, APC national chairman. Below are photos.     